	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;331&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;796px&#34;
	
&gt;
以bearing_1_1为例的csv详细数据如下：
&lt;img src=&#34;https://gogopaopao.github.io/newstack/newstack/p/%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E8%BD%B4%E6%89%BF%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%9B%86%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/img/csv%E8%AF%A6%E6%83%85_bearing_1_1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;542&#34;
